column5: What bay are you in? I know LOTW well. I'll actually be up there in a month.
Thats Eleanor lake. Right near big grassy first nations

Side of the house nice lil 16 ft that comes with the propertyview from front stepsto the south of the houseview from the kids room upstairsshoreline view on the west side of the lawnanother lawn shot property also has a few storage sheds, a riding lawn mower, a canoe, a paddle boat, a horseshoe pit, 2 nice apple trees, and a blueberry rock(through a trail to the east side of the property).
Ahh, I see. Southernish shore. I'm not familiar with that area. I fish from kenora to Sioux narrows and west to clear water bay. No doubt it will be beautiful. Tons of fish too
AWESOMENESS Rick….very excited for you….that looks amazing!  The fishing should be epic to say the least, looking forward to your Gopro masterpiece now.

Thanks simon!!! Gotta head up with a load this weekend and get that lawn mowed now lol. Gonna be a long two weeks to move out whats left there, move are stuff up, all while working and getting the kiddos to school haha. Looking forward to it though:)
jealous  yup jealous
That is fabulous, and GOOD ON YOU!!!!  Doug

And then the worst news possibly ever... Septic/electrical need work and wont be ready until late august or September:( good news is we can still utilize the property until then(weekend etc). Also cut a deal to help maintain the outside and free rent for two months once its good to go. Bad news, again, is will have a new house in our current area by October by the sounds of it:(
you could always sub-let...............

Amazingly happy:) we just got an offer to take a lakefront house on LOTW:) amazing property too. It would be temporary, as the owners are looking to sell, but rent throught the summer/fall. This might be too good to resist. I'm already marking spots lol. Be awesome if this pans out from now till fall
Sounds like an offer of a lifetime !!
Almost one million acres of water and no fish   some guys have all the luck
Ahhhh LOTW is ugly and there's terrible fishin.....maybe you could give me that info And I'll take one for the team
Some have all the luck! Sounds great !
I'll find out tomorrow night. I'm pretty restless already lol. Comes with some complications regarding work but oh well. There is even a nice boat that we are free to use;) awesome
People like you piss me off. I hope it works out for you.
Got the place!!!!!!! And dirt cheap to add. I'll be fishing LOTW by this time next weekend:)
Thats sweet.  Someone to give Simon a run for his money.

Oh i forgot crappies too:) the only shame is leaving. We might only be there a year or so. So well have to take full advantage and fish hard!!!!!!  Thanks for the replies guys:) i hope to provide some awesome reports
I am jealous and happy for you.
I can't be the first to suggest a G2G???
the property is on the upper left hand corner  where you see the drive way circular road. Just to piss off some city folks lol Quickly scanning for GPS coords.... Enjoy it!
I am happy for you, but also hate you and you ought to be ashamed of yourself
Do you need any new friends???  I'm already looking forward to your reports, what a fishery
Okay, OFC G2G in the making for sure!!!  Hope you get it, sounds awesome!
Oh my work cant end soon enough lol
I need to plan my (self invited) trip to meet you in person....
